snippet.title: Fake activism, Black Lives Matter, LGBT, DV, and Amber Heard Fallout
snippet.description:
Another very frank discussion about the Amber/Johnny Depp fiasco from the perspective of how much damage she’s done to the #MeToo #DomesticViolence and #LGBT awareness movements. Fake activism is not activism by any means! When someone uses trending hashtags in spokesperson roles, but acts like a closet racist/homophobe/abuser behind closed doors, it bears attention. By no means should we prop up these people and allow them to profit off of the publicity and the attention that they gain.

•For more info on how her friends are incriminated in their strange fraud, see Incredibly Average’s post here: https://youtu.be/phtD_zWn8e4
